    Enum containing the main types of focus measures.
    Author:
    royer

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      Correlative
      Correlative focus measures estimate sharpness by evaluation the spatial auto-correlation of images.
      Differential
      Differential focus measures are based on local differential operators such as first n seocnd order finite diffrences, sobel operators, etc...
      Spectral
      Spectral focus measures estimate image sharpness by analyzing the frequency content of images.
      Statistic
      Statistical focus measures are based on statistics such as average brightness, standard deviation, kurtosis, etc...
